1
00:00:00,100 --> 00:00:01,433
Let's watch it work.

2
00:00:01,383 --> 00:00:02,933
This is the Immortals bubble.

3
00:00:02,933 --> 00:00:06,516
I type one sentence — build me a weekly digest of new AI research.

4
00:00:06,516 --> 00:00:11,725
Instantly it assembles a team — you can see the plan as a small flowchart: research, then critique, then build.

5
00:00:11,725 --> 00:00:13,450
Then it goes quiet and works.

6
00:00:13,450 --> 00:00:16,200
Silence is the default — no firehose of pings.

7
00:00:16,200 --> 00:00:19,233
A live counter shows the routine decisions it is handling on its own.

8
00:00:19,233 --> 00:00:24,691
It interrupts me exactly once — for a genuine judgment call — and notes that it held back nine routine choices to ask this one.

9
00:00:24,691 --> 00:00:28,375
I answer, and it finishes: a verified report, stamped with who did what.

10
00:00:28,375 --> 00:00:30,525
Now — a hard cut to the dashboard.

11
00:00:30,525 --> 00:00:32,166
Because this is not a mockup.

12
00:00:32,166 --> 00:00:35,816
Here is a real run: the actual plan, the event timeline, the cost.

13
00:00:35,816 --> 00:00:37,133
Fully auditable.

